lead_paragraph: "Nerds," a new musical about the tech giants Bill Gates and Steve Jobs, has scuttled plans for its spring Broadway debut and plans to tour instead.

headline.main: Musical 'Nerds' Will Not Open on Broadway
headline.print_headline: Musical 'Nerds' Will Not Open on Broadway
